quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  9,14,"Fight them, so God may punish them at your hands and disgrace them, and support you against them, and heal the breasts of believing folk"
  9,15,"and remove the fury from their hearts. God turns to anyone He wishes; God is Aware, Wise"
  9,16,"Or do you reckon you will be abandoned once God knows which of you have struggled, and did not adopt anyone as an ally besides God, His messenger and believers? God is Informed anything you do"
  9,17,"Associators must not frequent God´s mosques since they act as witnesses for their own disbelief. Those [people will find] their actions will miscarry and they will remain forever in the Fire"
  9,18,"Only someone who believes in God and the Last Day, keeps up prayer, pays the welfare tax and dreads only God [Alone], shall frequent God´s mosques. Perhaps those may be the ones who submit to guidance"
  9,19,"Have you made those giving pilgrims something to drink a care of the Hallowed Mosque just like someone who believes in God and the Last Day, and struggles on for God´s sake? They are not equal before God; God does not guide such wrongdoing folk"
  9,20,"Those who believe and migrate, and struggle for God´s sake with their property and person stand much higher in rank with God. Those will be triumphant"